# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# .gitignore template for CLS syntax repositories
#
# Purpose: keep survey data, derived datasets etc 
# or other sensitive files OUT of version control.  
# Folders or files contained in this list will not be tracked by GitHub  
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------

# 1) Ignore entire data directories
#    – Users place raw files in data/raw/
#    – Scripts write outputs to data/derived/
data/*
data/raw/*
data/derived/*

# 2) Common statistical-package data files (Stata, SPSS, SAS, R, Arrow)
*.dta       # Stata
*.sav       # SPSS
*.sas7bdat  # SAS
*.xpt       # SAS transport files
*.rds       # R single-object files
*.RData     # R workspaces
*.feather   # Feather/Arrow
*.parquet   # Parquet columnar files

# 3) Other file types 
*.csv 
*.tab
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.ods

# 4) Compressed archives 
*.zip
*.gz
*.bz2
*.xz
*.7z
*.rar

# 5) Database dumps and binaries
*.sql
*.sqlite
*.db
*.mdb
*.accdb

# 6) Logs, caches, temporary or IDE artefacts
*.log
*.tmp
*.cache
.Rhistory
.Rproj.user/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# End of template
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------
